attributes.action: Set up a panel to support reviews into attacks on or deaths of social workers
attributes.background: The Government should set up a panel which supports local authorities to review  cases where a social worker or safeguarding professional is attacked or killed while working. The panel could also conduct wider reviews to help improve local authority practices.
